{"tid":1725240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒vs選舉戰","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:04.000Z","uid":116823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"371c2ba95ae81e8a7aafa549fe7f5dfc8146a279","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"其實而家政府擺明裝個陷阱喎<br />\n成日又封地鐵又唔開隧道<br />\n根本政府都有心玩野<br />\n唔明點解會覺得政府驚經濟差<br />\n佢根本都唔撚驚<br />\n反而區議會選舉係一次變相公投<br />\n如果泛民今鋪輸撚左，即係間接承認特區政府合法性<br />\n全香港都含撚<br />\n係好撚樣衰<br />\n相反，如果泛民贏出區選，係等如大大巴打鳩政府<br />\n全世界都知香港政府再冇香港人支持，失去合法性<br />\n到時再向政府施壓，過左死線就成立臨時政府<br />\n<br />\n所以，而家最重要唔係攬炒，係打選舉戰<br />\n唔差在一時<br />\n將怒火谷晒去選票度<br />\n少啲出量，多啲文宣你地老豆老母<br />\n唔撚好再比賣港賊贏啦，好唔好？"},{"pid":"8f8401cb0a4b0910530d34036a074d97c6ddacad","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"推（1/10）"},{"pid":"7cb4d55e929f75c2383ff3027ee6527a7677ac79","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"推（香港加油）"},{"pid":"1554a511ebf9e2409b9478ac8a543dd8b09547c7","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"8874eadbf9ac1f8a874229e9b84d4f5795c67895","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"40638827ed7e814b7eb9d62b46a68c965adc8b7a","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"35baefe464ebaf0afdd76e39cc40f661e1cba826","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"f1692207246b6e3e4b1b0ff22c099b222fd68d3a","tid":1725240,"uid":116823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"推7/10"},{"pid":"47b8afa6764c8120958d383d2827723df68a9e83","tid":1725240,"uid":224303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"攬炒同選舉唔係mutually exclusive<br />\n和理整文宣唔會冇時間<br />\n反而要keep 住係unrest，呢件事先會繼續係一件事<br />\n政府好明顯係打民意<br />\n想分化我地搞柒件事<br />\n請叻人上嚟分化破壞士氣就係啦<br />\n支持要谷文宣<br />\n推"}]}